node.text:
Man man man , since I have left Dallas the amount of new family members that have joined is actually OUT OF POCKET. What I have noticed lately is that one of the biggest obstacles to making lots of money is not a lack of good ideas or opportunities or time , or that we’re too slovenly or stupid . It’s that we refuse to give ourselves permission to become rich . We refuse to take the opportunities we see right in front of our face , we get all the signs that’s we need to hop on the opportunities and we still won’t. You just state all these excuses, and an excuse is nothing but a challenge that you’ve given your power too. You have two choices , You can have your ego or have your dreams. Which one are you choosing 👀🥺 #London2020
#itllallmakesense
#c50OTFW
